  <brief_title>Study of ISIS 301012 (Mipomersen) in Heterozygous Familial Hypercholesterolemia Subjects on Lipid Lowering Therapy</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Phase 2, Double-Blind, Placebo-Controlled, Dose Escalation Study to Assess the Safety, Efficacy, and Pharmacokinetics of ISIS 301012 as Add-on Therapy in Heterozygous Familial Hypercholesterolemia Subjects</official_title>
  <sponsors>
