  <source>Kastle Therapeutics, LLC</source>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The aim of this study is to assess the safety and efficacy of varying doses of ISIS 301012
      (mipomersen) as add-on therapy in subjects with Heterozygous Familial Hypercholesterolemia
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
